https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=14300	14880
芬兰手机巨头诺基亚公司<a href="http://yro.slashdot.org/story/09/10/22/1541220/Nokia-Sues-Apple-For-Patent-Infringement-In-iPhone">起诉苹果</a>，<a href="http://www.nokia.com/press/press-releases/showpressrelease?newsid=1349562">声称</a>iPhone手机侵犯了诺基亚的项10专利，谴责苹果公司试图“<a href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/business/2009/10/091022_nokia_apple_patents.shtml">免费搭乘诺基亚创新的便车</a>”。<i>
